		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Top screenshot: Showing the title screen, and a dummy Mode Selection screen that isn't programmed yet.
<br />Still isn't drawing the rockets yet.
<br />Mice and cats stay put until you press a button, then the action starts.
<br /><img src="http://img413.imageshack.us/img413/1699/chuchuyay.gif" alt="Image" />
<br />
<br />Bottom screenshot: OAM cycling from hell!
<br /><img src="http://img171.imageshack.us/img171/8121/oamcycling2.gif" alt="Image" />
<br />
<br />These mice are not animated by bankswitching in the screenshots where they aren't moving forward.  They are animated by updating the nametables.
<br />
<br />Screenshots best viewed in Firefox.  Chrome slows them down.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
